A towering ancient oak tree with its trunk split into distinct growth rings, each ring glowing with a different vibrant color representing evolution through time, roots transforming into flowing streams of luminescent data patterns, set against a twilight forest backdrop with fireflies carrying tiny geometric shapes, the tree's canopy bursting with fresh spring leaves on one side gradually transitioning to crystalline digital fractals on the other, Studio Ghibli style with soft watercolor textures, warm amber and cool teal color palette, dreamy atmospheric perspective with gentle mist weaving between smaller surrounding trees, conveying growth, transformation, and the beautiful progression from organic origins toward something more refined and powerful
